text: Magdalena Czyszczoń (born 4 March 1995) is a Polish female speed skater. She competed in the women's 16 lap mass start event during the 2018 Winter Olympics. == References == Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female speed skaters Category:Speed skaters at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Olympic speed skaters of Poland Category:Sportspeople from Zakopane
